.SH "EXTRA ARGUMENTS"
.sp
This driver support the following extra optional settings in the \fBups.conf\fR(5)\&.
.sp
\fBbattext = n\fR \- (default = 0, no extra battery, where n = Ampere*hour )
.sp
\fBprgshut = 1\fR \- (default = 0, no programmable shutdown )
